Subject: [PATCH] feat: reset-gdtf endpoint and 1:1 custom mesh Orbit bake

- POST /api/fixtures/:id/reset-gdtf discards user edits and re-imports from
  GDTF Share (carryEdits:false) or the stored local GDTF package
- Custom replaced models (metadata.replaced) skip glTF wrap/scale in Orbit bake
- Mesh-offset rotation is ignored for custom replaced models in Orbit
